ACT:
 Code of Criminal Procedure, ss. 165, 537---Reasons for search not recorded--Alleged illegality of search on this ground does not give to accused right to obstruct subsequent investigation by physical assault and wrongful confinement of person conducting investigation--Conviction of those who do so under s. 353 and 342 I.P.C. is justified.
 
